Fix this in BOTH `app/(tabs)/(home)/index.ios.tsx` AND `app/(tabs)/(home)/index.tsx`:

1. Import AsyncStorage at the top: `import AsyncStorage from '@react-native-async-storage/async-storage';`

2. Replace the `hasRegisteredThisSession` ref guard logic. Instead of only checking the ref, also check AsyncStorage for a persisted key. Use the key `push_token_registered_<memberId>` so it's per-member (handles account switching).

